    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Activity 1.1.1 Develop detailed design and cost estimate for solar energy systems in 5communities in Surkhet DistrictActivity 1.1.2 Deployment of solar pumping technology and construction of Multiple Water System (MUS) system in 4 communities and solar microgrid with flood warning system in 1 community.Activity 1.2.1 Mobilise finance for Solar energy project construction through partners/stakeholders in 5 communitiesActivity 1.2.2 Link community institutions to government agriculture bodies in 4 Solar MUS communitiesActivity 2.1.1 Establish/ revitalise economically sustainable committee institutions with legal status to own and manage the system and build their capacity Activity 2.2.1 Develop and implement water source conservation and protection plan, and water distribution system and management plan using participatory method.Activity 2.2.2 Install real time monitoring system (meters at the supply end) to measure and monitor the performance of the solar pumping system.Activity 3.1.1 Organise micro irrigation and high value crop production training.Activity 3.2.1 Identify markets in the field of agriculture and link them with community.Activity 4.1.1 Conduct awareness raising campaign on health and hygiene in the community and schools​."
      },
      "ne": null
